Bootstrap: docker
From: sysstacks/mers-ubuntu:v0.3.0

%post
    apt-get -y autoremove --purge
    apt-get -y clean

%test
    ffmpeg -version

%environment
    export LC_ALL=C

%runscript
    python

%help
    Intel Media Reference Stack v0.3.0 with Ubuntu 20.04 and OpenVINO toolkit, Intel Media SDK, FFmpeg, GStreamer, and various audio/video codecs. Based on the official Intel sysstacks/mers-ubuntu:v0.3.0 Docker image.
